The paper deals with optimization problems related to belief networks, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML) applications. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely categories. The paper also involves the use of directed acyclic graphs (DAGs), which are a fundamental data structure in computer science and data science, making cs.DS a likely category as well. The paper also discusses the reconfiguration and combination of BNs, which are relevant topics in the fields of systems integration (cs.SI) and information theory (cs.IT).
